room_title: Escape room "Payday" by Panic Escape Room in Chicago
room_address: 990 Grand Canyon Pkwy Hoffman Estates, IL 60169
room_description:
A-List jewelers is home to some of the most prominent A-List celebrities from Robert Downey Jr. to Kim Kardashian.
But this is no ordinary jewelry store you have an inside tip that a large rare diamond is worth it all! But you are not the only one to hear about it a world class thief is also en route you have 60mins to beat him to the punch as well as avoid the authorities.
